heres, accreting black-hole coronae and jets\nin XRBs and AGN, magnetospheres of magnetars, and Gamma-Ray Bursts. Finally,\nthis Chapter discusses the most critical open questions and outlines the\ndirections for future research in this exciting new frontier of plasma\nastrophysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2015 08:57:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-09"}
